processingCommand.script:
Echo on
IF "${DateOverrideFile}" EQU "" (
  ${XT_COPYFILE} from="${SourceFileName}" to="${TargetFileName}" ${CopyOptions}
) ELSE (
  ${XT_COPYFILE} from="${SourceFileName}" to="${TargetFileName}" datefile=${DateOverrideFile} ${CopyOptions}
)
Echo Off
set retcode=%errorlevel%
echo CopyFile ended with return code: %retcode%
IF %retcode% EQU 0 GOTO NORMALFLOW
GOTO ERRORFLOW
:NORMALFLOW
set resexe=0
GOTO END
:ERRORFLOW
set resexe=1
GOTO END
:END
exit %resexe%
